Get Inspired: The FA People's Cup Best Bits

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
There were tears of joy and tears of sadness, reunions of old friends, new friendships made, winners, losers and several dramatic penalty shootouts. This was the FA People's Cup 2015.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
