Over three action-packed rounds, 30,000 players were whittled down to 11 winning teams, who won the opportunity of a lifetime - to be presented with a giant winners cup on the pitch at Wembley during the FA Cup Final.
We hope you've loved the FA People's Cup as much as we have. Check out this video of some of the many, many brilliant moments from the tournament.
